{
  "stem": "268.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we marched until sundown.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it's-- and we're-- there was a big barn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They herded us like a bunch of cattle or sheep into a barn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But the barn could only hold so many.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And by the time my turn came, the doors were shut.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we must have been probably 200 or 300 left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we spent the night outside, which in a way, it was probably better because I heard there were a lot of killings inside and a lot-- a lot of hoarding and stealing.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they would cut someone's throat for a piece of bread or-- so we-- I remember waking-- waking up the next day-- the next day at dawn and-- and covered with snow, the first time in my life, I was-- I was ever covered in-- with snow instead of a blanket.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we got up and marched farther and not think about no colds, no sniffles, no, you know, no aspirins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we marched until we came-- this march took about almost three days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we came to a camp called the [GERMAN], which was the-- we were all satellite camps under that particular camp, which was called Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a-- a death camp with crematoria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and all these camps that I described previously I-- were under the authority of that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This was like a mother camp, you know, a [GERMAN], the main camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There, this was a horrible place, just like a warehouse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was no-- no more going to work, no regular-- that camp made-- made the regular camp look-- look-- look like Club Med, to-- to-- to use a comparison, because there-- it-- we had, there were like three-- three bunks high in the one camp.",
      "word_count": 45
    }
  ],
